flowchart TD
    A([👤 User]) -->|Shares bill image path/URL| B[UserProxy Agent]
    B -->|Initiates chat with image input| C[GroupChatManager]

    C -->|Routes to| D[BillProcessingAgent]
    D -->|Reads & analyzes image| E{Extract Line Items}
    E -->|Categorize into:\nGroceries · Dining · Utilities\nShopping · Entertainment · Other| F[Categorized Expense List + JSON]

    F -->|Passes structured data| C
    C -->|Routes to| G[ExpenseSummarizationAgent]
    G -->|Aggregates totals per category| H{Spending Analysis}
    H -->|Identifies highest spend\nFlags unusual items\nProvides insights| I[Expense Summary Report]

    I -->|Final output delivered to| A

    style A fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style B fill:#2196F3,color:#fff
    style C fill:#9C27B0,color:#fff
    style D fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
    style G fill:#F44336,color:#fff
    style I fill:#009688,color:#fff
